text: Puycapel is a commune in the Cantal department in south-central France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Calvinet and Mourjou.Arrêté préfectoral 12 December 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Cantal department ==References== Category:Communes of Cantal Category:States and territories established in 2019 Category:Populated places established in 2019
title: Puycapel
